---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<footer class="border-t mt-24">
  <div class="container py-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4 text-sm">
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-display font-semibold mb-3">
        <span class="grid h-8 w-8 place-items-center rounded-md bg-tane-primary text-white">T</span>
        <span>Trendora</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-tane-muted">Tu marca activa en redes, sin estar tú.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-3">Producto</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-tane-muted">
        <li><a href="/#features" class="hover:text-foreground">Funcionalidades</a></li>
        <li><a href="/precios" class="hover:text-foreground">Precios</a></li>
        <li><a href="/changelog" class="hover:text-foreground">Changelog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/roadmap" class="hover:text-foreground">Roadmap</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-3">Recursos</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-tane-muted">
        <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-foreground">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/casos-de-exito" class="hover:text-foreground">Casos de éxito</a></li>
